file. You can also use DEFAULT.
• For the _v2 function:
• The fourth argument is the start time for retrieving the logs - for example:
'2028-01-02T03:04:05Z'. You can also use DEFAULT.
• The fifth argument is the end audit time.
• It is recommended that you use the _v2 function - use the fourth and fifth
argument can provide performance improvements.
