version 8. If you do not have it installed, install it, then close Visual Studio
Code and re-open it.
o dab init --database-type mssql --config dab-config.json --
connection-string "Server=…;Connection Timeout=30;"
o The connection-string should be taken from the Azure SQL
Database (Settings – Connection strings).
o dab add Address --source SalesLT.Address --permissions
"anonymous:read“
 46. Create configuration files for Data API builder (DAB)

o dab add Customer --source SalesLT.Customer --permissions
"anonymous:read"
o dab add CustomerAddress --source SalesLT.CustomerAddress --
permissions "anonymous:read"
o If the table, query or stored procedure has already been
added, you can use “dab update” to update it.
