development.
o dab start
o When you want to end it, press Ctrl and C.
• In a web browser, enter:
o http://localhost:5000/health
o This will only work if mode is development.
o http://localhost:5000/api/Address (this uses the REST API).
o This will give you the first 100 records.
o The last bit is a “nextLink”, which gives you a link to the next
100 records (paging).
